                                <div id="faq_accordion_1" class="accordion-content accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="faq_accordion_heading_1" data-bs-parent="#accordionFaq">
                                    <div class="accordion-body"><p>There are no hidden fees at Plus500. Plus500 is mainly compensated for its services through the spread. For more information, please read: <a href="../tradingacademy/faq/feescharges/doyouchargeanyfees.html">“Do you charge any trading fees?”</a> </p>   </div>
